# --- Public-repo privacy hardening ---
# `data/` is a private git submodule (real holdings). Never vendored here.
# Rendered mini-site pages are generated from that private data and may contain
# real positions/NAV/P/L. Build locally with tools/generate_site.py; never commit.
# (The app shell web/index.html lives under web/ and stays tracked.)
/*.html

# --- Secret / credential belt-and-suspenders ---
# `secrets.env` and `*.env` are covered above; the rest is defense in depth so a
# stray credential file can never be staged by accident.
.env
.env.*
*.secret
*.secrets
secrets.*
*credentials*.json
*.token
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.keystore
id_rsa
id_rsa.pub
id_ed25519
*.ppk

# Scratch / generated junk
*.tmp
COMMIT_MSG*
PR_BODY*
